metadata.name: Gold Torrent, Inc.
metadata.description: Gold Torrent, Inc. engages in acquisition and exploration of mining properties in the United States. It holds 70% interest in the Lucky Shot gold project located in Alaska. The company was formerly known as Celldonate Inc. and changed its name to Gold Torrent, Inc. in January 2014. Gold Torrent, Inc. was founded in 2006 and is based in Boise, Idaho.
